{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.13,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Google gave away a model that cost hundreds of millions to build.",
      "checksum": "sha256:32fd4e65db4b5238f5a202d703261265c0d8d327474bafc33e0089fe1fa25e6f",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "No subscription. No A P I fee. No revenue share.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eaa64b2c3e497c7e416b00268f110112dc24301b14d0732e749f3f4448814b6f",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Either Google lost its mind. Or something just changed in A I that most people missed.\n\nFor 2 years, A I meant one thing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1aa47783f42d07ca58b9b59b33756eece0d536e0e7a587f8c0b3ce0772b7ba38",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 7.7090249433106575,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 22
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "You called an A P I. You paid per token.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a921051278f2dca1035a1874507027d4558d138064852a19eb98e351073faaa0",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "You got a bill at the end of the month. Then in January 2025, DeepSeek shipped an open model that wiped 600 billion off Nvidia in a single day.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5fb6a65a5ec505da58fa9775c2dcfd4370fa22223e7e02488b0f683e61287d56",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 10.031020408163265,
      "word_count": 29,
      "words_offset": 56
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "The open weight tier had arrived. You download the weights.",
      "checksum": "sha256:79902cf0c501b72e67f93c4d956c0d21100de13aca41a94998d647e1da1289b3",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 85
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "You run them on your own hardware. The marginal cost collapses to electricity.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3f6edb49706aa739a34946bd61b79afea4487d84184262bb99c8adf2a9d2d87f",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 95
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "At scale, that is 10 to 100 times cheaper.",
      "checksum": "sha256:be84e20adbe8830eb1da306ad7320fbb0465206f35ffbd22cc5ab88bb1ecc515",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 108
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Airbnb already moved significant workloads off OpenAI onto Qwen.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c899b533712166420860247900e1fb43ce27f6b71397715d45cd9721bd6109af",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "They just ran the numbers. Google is the only company playing in both lanes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9fed78fab99e46518867ef2ee50b8659b68b6a9160c10e01d61d84744aa7f550",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 126
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Gemini for closed. Gemma for open. So why give Gemma away free.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5bf9d9e2a4ff3201ef1b4f3e7e4f6222bec419abb32ef8587362b52f32436018",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 140
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "There are 3 stacked payoffs. Payoff 1. Commercial capture.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3cf36bb04cba65d1ff508e1c5802be9b3f2f1ff1ce8d88cb99211100d9fa9e84",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 152
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Gemma is free. The cloud rails are not. The moment you fine-tune or build an agent, you need infrastructure.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b54a793b84ff5b3b72dc17ed74dbd63071c5fa76f377c0aebfd83295f80656df",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 6.315827664399093,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 161
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Google parked Gemma 4 inside Google Cloud.",
      "checksum": "sha256:16fd7e9b7bec306c9a1fe991463ee1df2bbc2d464e81d1c5594dfb2f142ad6f0",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 180
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "T P U chips. Cloud Run. Sovereign cloud.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e30131ae42542922ca0f10baa20e2c7ce5ae5cf62eae1f59febaf2178bb418dd",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 187
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Last quarter, Google Cloud hit 17.7 billion in revenue.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bb88053c6625239ae85393fe46f177bacafec6e9b1f15c38ebf4b9be62360156",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 195
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Up 48 percent year-over-year. The smallest models also run on Android, Pixel, and Chrome.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1aabc8e3b74c790addc84215f591ea9428ac1ed7e9fb0496941cb98fad7c0fb9",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 5.061950113378685,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 204
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Payoff 2. Competitive denial. Over the past year, China shipped open weight models rivaling G P T-5 and Claude.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09e10e0f427065336e55dbd2aaf0ff076fb8f70ba04401a3c6e504e848eb8e5c",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 6.873106575963718,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 218
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Alibaba. DeepSeek. Moonshot. For any Western enterprise running A I on their own hardware, the best option was starting to look Chinese.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09f6c7dcf2b7a39be62976ce52b64a598d83caa3a667ed7d6a5ffc92b166c7ab",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 9.102222222222222,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 237
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Gemma 4 is Google planting a flag. A Western alternative built by a US company.",
      "checksum": "sha256:442e4174f4e963eb54c0debd5775c1761dda7855b91cc677b39144fa2e2f28ce",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 259
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Without the Chinese provider risk. And every time Gemma gets better, OpenAI and Anthropic lose pricing power.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5cf867357724dd2f1b09dd5b4e1da211d159b5f45501da67066b150708f11439",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 6.501587301587302,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 274
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Google can absorb that hit. They do not depend on token revenue.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b2992de9a600183ca688104f2bbe9391d3d9a6a1020f08a2ee1227368df00e91",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 291
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Payoff 3. Portfolio reinforcement. Gemma 4 shares research with Gemini 3.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a4a12e4309eac9a6e781dfd711a9de1877c082d22911d13344855cba9d46e8d6",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 303
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Every benchmark Gemma wins reinforces Gemini.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f6364c8ffa5e6008175dac721be5c65ea99909bd520bc592b1e9ee9cf0c05376",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 314
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "The free model sells the paid one. Gemma ships under Apache 2.0.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1cfc99f9c07cdfa8d28c3679996c2fdb8dcbef264290fa3c7ddb6d9b3dc3fbd3",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 320
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "The most permissive license in software.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a33e23eb224e79508f129c0635df2e0bcd235483c64bffe16c11fc9f295a92c7",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.089795918367347,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 332
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Every developer who builds on Gemma becomes fluent in Google's stack.",
      "checksum": "sha256:acf5c9f7d75f62bbdc07dee297ccaebcc67c261d42c6f0a726e98d27ba43cfd7",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 338
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "That same engineer writes the next 5 million dollar procurement decision.",
      "checksum": "sha256:032fb7b93085adc70d933e17ca8d1ed57511beb613b84c1310dffbe209a58d72",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 349
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Here is the shift. OpenAI cannot do this.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f5aa6d3368601a846915241265aa9b5b47164bcbcb0b84d5006d63b2b10876e6",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 360
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "No cloud. No T P Us. No Android. The model is their business.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07320abe07797dd7672e34b3b4e13ab42b4652333c1d26dbd2e5568a22ad3fa4",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 368
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Anthropic will not. They think open weights are too dangerous.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7a560cc81013e5946a8e82876d772e2decfde7b13ec022819e554422562939cc",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 381
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "Google is alone in playing both tiers. Stanford tracked the gap.",
      "checksum": "sha256:efd6690424285112a5f8650e5f463bab1f84c1d7d9917c0d75aef4f68599df66",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 391
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "It narrowed throughout 2024 and 2025. It briefly hit par.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3cf32846aab8d60d9f4bb71ec44935eeebd6447f7b1a43dfdcf48218ea7c09c9",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 402
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "This March, it widened back to 3 points.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c834c9714105d2e3a94bad174c0bcf228964d1b12f0d9a039d73cd7b17c357d3",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 412
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "So stop asking which A I is best. Ask which tier your workflow belongs in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0230381bdbd5f00b29f9f38aab672d977a05feb2b86f34e94d8a5eeb59d2c3a2",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 420
    }
  ]
}